  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, open label study of Nilotinib in CML patients PH + with imatininb resistant in
      blast crisis, accelerated phase or chronic phase. The main purpose is evaluate the safety and
      efficacy of Nilotinib.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
